{"name": "rd-api-py", "metadata": {"name": "rd-api-py", "version": "0.4.0", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "", "license": "", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests", "python-dotenv"], "summary": "Real Debrid API Library for Python", "upload_time": 1695928881}, "documentation": ["# rd_api_py\n\nReal Debrid API Library for Python\n\n## Installation\n\nInstall the package\n\n```bash\npython -m pip install rd_api_py\n```\n\nSet environment variables in `.env` in `rd_refresh` or your script\n\n```bash\nRD_APITOKEN=\"your_token_here\"\nSLEEP=100 # Delay (ms) between requests - optional, default recommended\nLONG_SLEEP=5000 # Long delay (ms) every 500 requests - optional, default recommended\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nAll operations are supported - see examples directory\n\n```python\nfrom rdapi import RD\n\nRD = RD()\n\nprint(RD.system.time().content)\nprint(RD.user.get().json())\nprint(RD.torrents.get(limit=10, page=1).json())\n\nimport os\nfilepath = '/path/to/bbb.torrent'\nprint(RD.torrents.add_file(filepath=filepath).json())\n\n# etc...\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "rdapi", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "rdapi.RD", "xref": {"fqname": "rdapi.rdapi.RD", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "rdapi.rdapi", "documentation": ["!/usr/bin/env python3"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "rdapi.rdapi.RD", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "rdapi.rdapi.RD.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rdapi.rdapi.RD.get", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**options", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rdapi.rdapi.RD.post", "asynch